title: Zabby and Elf's Stone Soup
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Salad bar, Take-out, Bakery, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Veg menu items includes seitan pot pie, tandoori tempeh, steamed kale and brown rice, daily vegetarian and vegan specials, plus salad bar with greens from local farms. Breads and pastries are baked in its open kitchen daily.
